relatedProducts.name: Pumped Up Kicks
relatedProducts.slogan: Faster than a just about anything
relatedProducts.description: The Pumped Up serves up crisp court style with a modern look. These shoes show off tennis-whites shades and are constructed with a supple leather upper and a classic rubber cupsole.

relatedProducts.name: YEasy 350
relatedProducts.description: These stretchy knit shoes show off asymmetrical lacing and a big sculpted rubber midsole. In a nod to adidas soccer heritage.

relatedProducts.name: Summer Shoes
relatedProducts.slogan: A risky call in the spring or fall
relatedProducts.description: Low-top panelled buffed leather and mesh sneakers. Sizing embroidered in black at round toe. Tonal lace-up closure. Pull-loop and rubberized style name at padded tongue. Padded collar. Pull-loop at heel collar. Logo embroidered in black at outer side. Tonal treaded rubber sole. Tonal stitching.

relatedProducts.name: Camo Onesie
relatedProducts.description: The So Fatigues will wake you up and fit you in. This high energy camo will have you blending in to even the wildest surroundings.

relatedProducts.name: Morning Joggers
relatedProducts.description: Whether you're a morning person or not.  Whether you're gym bound or not.  Everyone looks good in joggers.
